Vcs-Git: http://git.code.sf.net/p/metpx/git

Package: metpx-sarracenia
Architecture: all 
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, rabbitmq-server (>= 3.3.5), ${python:Depends}, python3-pkg-resources, python3-amqplib, python3-pyinotify, python3-psutil
Recommends: python3-paramiko
Homepage: http://metpx.sourceforge.net
Description: Meteorological Product Exchanger
 A utility that consumes AMQP message containing
 URL of newly posted products on http://dd.weather.gc.ca and
 downloads them in specified directories. Both products and directories
 are user configurable.
 Developed at the Shared Services Canada
